<p style="Normal" xid="539" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">2. В </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">pages_controller</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> добавим методы </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">pages</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> и </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">about</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="541" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">3. В </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">routes.rb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> добавим пути:   </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">get ‘terms”  =&gt; pages#terms</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> и  </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="542" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">get  ‘about’  =&gt; pages#about</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="526" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">4. Добавим представления, заходим в папку </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">views/pages</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> и создаем </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">terms.html.erb </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">и </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">about.html.erb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">.   в одном прописываем </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">&lt;h1&gt;pages &lt;/h1&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> , в другом </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">&lt;/h1&gt; about &lt;/h1&gt;</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="543" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">теперь можно откыть эти документы по ссылке  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">/about</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">  и </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">/pages</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">.</c></p>
