<p style="Normal" xid="751" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">    create	read	  update  delete</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="752" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:14pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="753" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:14pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">new 		.find(3)  .update   destroy</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:14pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="754" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:14pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.save 		.all</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:14pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="746" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">.create		.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">where(filter)</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="756" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="757" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">﻿<br/> REST (Representational state transfer) ﻿– <c></c><c props="font-weight:normal">это стиль архитектуры программного обеспечения для распределенных систем, таких как World Wide Web, который, как правило, используется для построения веб-служб. Термин REST был введен в 2000 году Роем Филдингом, одним из авторов HTTP-протокола. Системы, поддерживающие REST, называются RESTful-системами</c>.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="760" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">﻿<c></c><c props="font-weight:normal">HTTP действие над данными задается с помощью методов: </c><c props="font-weight:bold">GET</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> (получить), </c><c props="font-weight:bold">PUT </c><c props="font-weight:normal">(добавить, заменить), </c><c props="font-weight:bold">POST</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> (добавить, изменить, удалить), </c><c props="font-weight:bold">DELETE</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> (удалить). Таким образом, действия </c><c props="font-weight:bold">CRUD (Create-Read-Updtae-Delete)</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> могут выполняться как со всеми 4-мя методами, так и только с помощью </c><c props="font-weight:bold">GET</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> и </c><c props="font-weight:bold">POST</c><c props="font-weight:normal">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="765" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="762" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">В нашем случае за </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">REST</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> отвечает два ключевых слова </c><c props="font-weight:bold">resource, resources.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="764" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-align:left; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; color:000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt"><c props="font-weight:normal">Существет 6 методов </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">hero.rb</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="793" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c><c props="font-weight:normal">для </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">resource, и 7 </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">методов для </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">resources.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="766" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Можно также создавать вложенные сущности :</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="767" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">resources do</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="768" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">    resource</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">s</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="763" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">end.<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="769" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="770" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">Полезные сайты для веб разработки.<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="771" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">plunker - <c></c><c props="font-weight:normal">просто вводится в строку браузера.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="773" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="774" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">Тестирование вашего приложение с помощью гема RSPEC</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="776" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Для того чтобы протестировать приложение сначала нужно установить гем rspec</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="777" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">В консоли набираем:</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="778" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">gem install rspec</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="779" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Создадим программу которую будем тестироввать</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="781" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">назовем проект </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">demo_spec</c><c props="font-weight:normal">. В этой проекте создадим два файла </c><c props="font-weight:bold">hero.rb</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> и </c><c props="font-weight:bold">hero_spec.rb</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="783" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">В hero.rb пропишем программу которую будем тестировать, а в hero_spec.rb напишем тесты для этой программы.</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="784" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"> </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="794" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="795" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="796" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:normal">   </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="797" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">hero.rb</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="798" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="787" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">class Hero</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="788" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">   def initialize(name, health = 100)</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="789" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">   @name = name.capitalize</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="792" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold">   @health= health</c><c props="font-weight:bold"></c></p>
