<p style="Normal" xid="815" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">теперь напишем тесты для этой программы:</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="817" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-align:left; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; color:000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt"><c props="font-weight:normal">hero_spec.rb</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="821" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="820" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:bold"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">require ‘./hero.rb ' -  </c><c props="font-weight:normal">подключаем файл с тестироваемой программой</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="822" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="819" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">  слово </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">describe</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> создает как бы инициализацию теста обычно с названием класса тестируемого обьекта он будет включать в себя все тестируемые методы данного обьекта и в случае ошибки выведется на </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="824" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="823" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">describe Hero do </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="827" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">сначало идет</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> it</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> который говорит нам что щас будет описываться метод, потом строка которая выражает действие которо должно подвердится.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="826" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">it “has a capitalized name” do </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> “has a capitalized name” в случае ошибки будет выведено на экран.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="828" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">hero = Hero.new ‘mike’ </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">  создаем обьект который будет тестироваться</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="825" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">expect(hero.name).to eql ‘Mike’ </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">  - тоесть ожидаем что метод .name Выдаст нам имя с большой буквы.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="759" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Вот как данная программа тестирования будет выглядеть</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="837" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="835" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-bottom:0.0000in; color:000000; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">require ‘./hero.rb '</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="740" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">describe Hero do</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="836" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">   it “has a capitalized name” do</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="839" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">   hero = Hero.new ‘mike’ </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="840" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">   expect(hero.name).to eql ‘Mike’</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="841" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">   end</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="842" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">end</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="843" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="832" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Теперь если набрать команду с консоли </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rspec hero_spec.rb  --color </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">, то она выдаст нам правильный ответ в зеленом цвете а неправильный в красном.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="833" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Точки в консоли показывают что тест пройден, а F показывает что в  тесте ошибка.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="834" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; text-position:normal; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; color:000000; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
