<p style="Normal" xid="1003" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">Мы создавали метод </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">article_params</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> позволяющей сохранить такие данные как </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">title</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> и </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">text.  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Такую же функцию надо сделать в </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">application</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> контроллере для того чтобы передать значения в базу данных для модели </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">User</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. правда это делаеться чуть по другому. Откроем </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">application_controller</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> и разберем строчки которые мы добавим.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1032" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1022" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">class ApplicationController &lt; ActionController::Base<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1023" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">  protect_from_forgery with: :exception<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1024" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left">  before_action :configure_permitted_parameters, if: :devise_controller?<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1025" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left">  <c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1026" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">   private<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1027" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1028" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left">  def configure_permitted_parameters<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1037" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">    devise_parameter_sanitizer.permit(:sign_in, keys: [:username])<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1031" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">end<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1033" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1034" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Разберем добавленные строчки:</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1035" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"> </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">before_action :configure_permitted_parameters, if: :devise_controller?  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Эта строчка говорит нам  о том  что это фильтр, который делает конфигурацию для разрешенных параметров(в данном случае это </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">username</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">), и запускается если в контроллере(</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">articles_controller</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">) стоит фильтр для авторизации:(</c>before_filter :authenticate_user!). </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1036" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Дальше видим сам приватный метод  который добавляет </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">username</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> для акшина </c><c props="font-weight:bold">sign_in</c><c props="font-weight:normal">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1055" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">	Теперь на м нужно отредактировать нашу форму авторизации </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">sign_up</c><c props="font-weight:normal">.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1058" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Во папке </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">views</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> нет странички которая отображала бы форму авторизации. Воспользуемся нашей командоай которая выводит все доступные генераторы </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1059" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">команда в консоли </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails g </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">выводит все доступные генераторы которыми можно воспользоваться.  Выбираем генератор </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails g devise:views . </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Теперь мы видим что создалась папка </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">devise</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> в нашей папке в </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">views</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. В папке </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">devise/registrations</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> находим файл </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">new.html.erb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> и добаляем после поля прописывающий email, такой код:</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1061" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">&lt;div class="field"&gt;<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1062" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">    &lt;%= f.label :username %&gt;&lt;br /&gt;<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1063" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left">    &lt;%= f.text_field  :username %&gt;<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1064" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">  &lt;/div&gt;<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1066" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Пропишем заодно и валидацию для поля </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">username</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> в модели </c><c props="font-weight:bold">User.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1067" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left">validates :username,:presence =&gt; true,:uniqueness =&gt; { :case_sensitive =&gt; false }<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1068" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">validates_format_of :username, with: /^[a-zA-Z0-9_\.]*$/<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1069" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Теперь исправим файл application.html.erb. Поменяем вывод почтового ящика </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1060" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> &lt;%= current_user.email %&gt; &lt;%= link_to 'Sign_out', destroy_user_session_path, </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1070" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">на вывод имени пользователя и добавим метод который позаботиться о том чтобы заглавная буква пользователя была с большой буквы:</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1071" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">hello &lt;%= current_user.username.capitalize %&gt; !!! &lt;%= link_to 'Sign_out', destroy_user_session_path. <c></c><c props="font-weight:normal">Теперь при авторизации выводится имя пользователя. То что нам и было нужно.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1057" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:normal">     Мы помним что для статьи мы создали фильтр который при обращении к  статьям, или отдельной написанной статьи, закрывал нам доступ полностью до тех пор пока мы не авторизируемся. Такие действия не совсем правильные, лучше оставить ресурсы для просмотра статьи, а запретить создание и редактирование статьи. Это легко можно сделать. Зайдем в аrticles_controller:</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1072" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">class ArticlesController &lt; ApplicationController<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1074" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">before_filter :authenticate_user!<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1056" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-align:left"><c props="font-weight:normal">Теперь исправим наш фильтр так чтобы он запрещал только действия </c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c props="font-weight:bold">create</c><c props="font-weight:normal"> и </c><c props="font-weight:bold">new</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1054" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">class ArticlesController &lt; ApplicationController<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1075" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c></c>before_filter :authenticate_user!, only: [:new, :create]</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1079" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-weight:normal">И добавим этот же фильтр для комментариев.</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1082" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">class CommentsController &lt; ApplicationController<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1080" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-decoration:none; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; margin-right:0.0000in; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left">before_filter :authenticate_user!, only: [ :create]<c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1077" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-weight:normal">Все задачу мы выполнили, теперь будут только заблокированы только выбранные акшины. Мы можем просматривать статью, а для создания новой статьи нам понадобиться регистрация, тоже относится и для комментариев.</c><c props="font-weight:normal"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1078" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-weight:normal"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1083" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">(Rubyschool lesson 44)</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1084" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1085" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Добавить Bootstrap в приложение.</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1086" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Всегда любой сайт с бутстрепом начинается с </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> &lt;div class = “container"&gt;. </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Это основной див в котором будут располагаться элементы бутстрапа. Дальше следущий по важности элемент идут ряды.  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;div class = “row” &gt;  . </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Рядов в отличии от контейнера может быть сколько угодно много. Если вы хотите сделать какое то количество столбцов, то эти столбцы должны быть внутри элементоа  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;div class = “row” &gt; </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">и никак иначе. Внутри элемента  raw мы должны добавить один или несколько столбцов. Чтобы добавить столбцы мы используем элемент </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">coll</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">. Выглядит этот элемент так: </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1088" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;div class = “coll-...-...&gt; . </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Вот как будет выглядеть страница со всеми этими элементами:</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1090" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1091" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;body&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1092" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">     &lt;div class="container"&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1093" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	&lt;div class="row"&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1094" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	         &lt;div class = “coll-xs-12“&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1095" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		     &lt;h1&gt; Hello Plunker! &lt;/h1&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1096" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	         &lt;/div&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1097" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	&lt;/div&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1099" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">     &lt;/div&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1100" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;/body&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1098" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1101" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Эти классы являются минимальным требованием правильного подхода к бутсрапу. Разберем подробнее элемент </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;div class = “coll-xs-12“&gt;  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">В бутстраме есть такой раздел который называеться  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Grid system </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">И там написано что вся решетка разделена на 12 столбцов.  Разберем подробнее  coll-xs :   XS обозначает размер они могут быть такими:</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1102" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">xs - самые маленькие; sm- маленькие; md- средние; lg- большие.  Большой маленький и средний это размер нашего экрана устройства. Это размер для смартфона, планшета.  Для больших экранов компьютера это размер lg. Все это сделано для технологии responsive design. Которая предусматривает  чтобы страница выглядела одинаково хорошо на разных устройствах будь то планшет, ноутбук или смартфон. Приведем пример адаптивного дизайна:</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1103" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1089" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;body</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1191" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">     &lt;div class="row"&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1192" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1193" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	&lt;div class ="col-sm4 col-xs-4</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1194" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">	    &lt;ul&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1195" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		&lt;li&gt;contact 1&lt;/li&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1196" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;li&gt;contact 2&lt;/li&gt;</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1197" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		&lt;li&gt;contact 3&lt;/li&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1198" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		&lt;li&gt;contact 4&lt;/li&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="1199" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">		&lt;li&gt;contact 5&lt;/li&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c></p>
